<title type="html"><![CDATA[12/15 (Thu.) Emotion management for health / Impromptu speech (Host: Lawrence)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=680&amp;p=708#p708"><![CDATA[
12/15 (Thu.) Emotion management for health / Impromptu speech (Host: Lawrence)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />--------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session1: Emotion and thought management<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.takingcharge.csh.umn.edu/how-do-thoughts-and-emotions-affect-health">https://www.takingcharge.csh.umn.edu/ho ... ect-health</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1, Do you agree emotional management is very important? Why?<br />2, What do you agree the most in this article?<br />3, Are you good or bad at emotional management? Please share your stories.<br />4, What causes your emotional storm in your life? How do you usually deal with them?<br />5. Free asking<br /><br /><br />Session 2: ‘impromptu discussion + impromptu speech’ <br />For impromptu discussion time (40 minutes), each person prepares one or two questions for the small group discussion.<br />For impromptu speech time (20 minutes), the host will pick some people to answer his questions or take turns. The purpose of impromptu speech (Table topic) is to train the speaker to give a speech without any preparation. <br />Speaking time is about 2 minutes.<br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Fri Dec 09, 2022 4:11 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
